      <scopecontent id="aspace_c8899c50a5f887199eee99cf6a49d3fa">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of photographs documenting the construction of Sterling Chemistry Laboratory at Yale. Includes two copies of a bound presentation album of construction photographs which proceed in reverse chronological order. Also included are exterior, interior, and aerial views, as well as shots of areas of the building requiring renovation work in 1962.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
